        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses Rugby and education in general. The enormous proportion of time spent on classics checks interest "in anything in which reasoning &amp; observation comes into play".</p>
            <p>Expresses shock and sympathy on learning of the deaths in WDF’s house.</p>
        </abstract>
